data.description: Move-in ready, super clean, modern and on-trend finishes throughout this charming pool home. Fantastic kitchen and laundry room shows big, has lovely cabinets with an abundance of storage, wall oven, flat cooktop, huge island, upgraded appliances, quartz countertops and built-in cubby space. Many upgrades throughout such as sprayed insulation in the attic, impact glass windows, closet organizers, fenced-in backyard, attractive ceiling fans and light fixtures. This 3 bedroom plus den/office, big pool, huge yard property is located in a desirable area and a must see!
